name: Barbara 2in1 Lora
description:
Brief

This is a multi-identifier Lora of Barbara, the lovely deaconess of the Church of Favonius and a prominent "idol" of Mondstadt.

Changing costume

I have included the 2 costumes in game, and you can easily switch between them with prompt:

  • barbara \(genshin impact\) for the default

  • barbara \(summertime sparkle\) \(genshin impact\) for the swimsuit

Works with weight 0.75~1

Since the model is not hard trained, the costume can be easily removed by simply put "nude" or "completely nude" in the prompt.

And for the costume, it is recommended that you put some prompts to emphasis, for example:

  • For default costume, put: twintails, blonde hair, frilled dress, hat, white pantyhose, bare shoulders,

  • For swimsuit, put: twintails, blonde hair, one-piece swimsuit, hat, etc.

Training:

4+8 epochs with high+low RL. for more details, please visit my hugging face page, I`ll post the training details and processes there: https://huggingface.co/okingjo/Multi-identifier_LORA_Model

Hope you like my model and use it to generate more great images!
